Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.92,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我问爸爸借了摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.14,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们多拍点东西来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.85,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是一如既往地烦啊 片桐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.30,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.33,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敦君等一会也来拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:06.42,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,庄一直叫音音「片桐」的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.70,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会感到不满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:10.84,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我高中毕业之后想被老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:13.12,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天使 小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:15.89,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.12,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过的确 被敦君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:23.40,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我的名字 我还是有点憧憬的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:27.75,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个那个 我们多拍点作纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:29.46,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再办个上映会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.23,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听起来很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.50,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.58,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,今日气候晴朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:39.53,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 太死板了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.52,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:45.70,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫入江小凪 是洼村老师的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.27,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.80,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 庄呢？他还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.56,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找找他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:02:02.10,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,音…音…音…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:03.82,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到敦君了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:05.30,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}音…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.79,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.05,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.60,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,音音音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.40,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:14.44,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.29,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敦君也快点来拍录像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.18,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 我说了我没兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:22.83,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是一份回忆啊 大家一起来拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.22,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小音真是天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:28.04,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才说了没兴趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.45,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好缠人 你是跟踪狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.38,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快走开 我真是超讨厌你这点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.48,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.99,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:51.39,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,老哥说他以后打死都绝对不说「讨厌」这个词了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:55.94,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他因为弄哭了片桐 差点就去切腹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.95,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是全力阻止他了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.95,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:06.69,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,片桐那之后也还挺精神的 应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.61,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋老哥真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.67,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然弄哭了小音 真是不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:18.20,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,音…音…音…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.95,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小音…真是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.85,akkun-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是…甜食？
